# Forbidden Patterns

- Business logic inside widgets
- Direct `SharedPreferences` usage in UI or domain
- Hardcoded secrets
- Shared mutable state outside StateNotifiers
- Massive widgets (>300 lines)
- Monolithic repositories
- Circular provider dependencies
- Untyped dynamic maps without models
- Silent catch blocks
- Duplicate serialization logic
- Framework leakage into domain
- Platform services in domain layer
- Hardcoded colors/durations outside theme/`AppAnimations`

